plot: The taxi driver who drove Margrethe Thormod and was the last person to see her alive, turns out to have connections to another victim as well, while suspicions about the Sonning couple also grow.

Saga and Henrik keep searching for a link between the murder victims. Lilian is reprimanded by her superiors. Dan finds out where his ex-wife and son are and causes trouble. The relationship between Saga and Henrik is tested to the limit and may have hit its breaking point.—CD
